high_descs: turn right and right again when you are standing in front of the island
pick up the glass  off of the table
put the glass in the refrigerator
take  the glass  out  of the refrigerator
put the glass bowl down on next to the stove on the left
anns.task_desc: put the glass on the floor to the left of the stove

high_descs: Walk around to the other side of the kitchen island.
Pick up the martini glass to the left of the lettuce.
Turn around and walk to the fridge.
Open the fridge door, put the glass in the fridge, close the door, open the door, take the glass out of the fridge, and close the door.
Turn right and look down at the cabinet below the counter to the left of the stove.
Open the cabinet door, put the glass inside the cabinet, and close the door.
anns.task_desc: To chill a martini glass and put it in the cabinet.

high_descs: Turn to your right and go to the wall, then turn to your right and go past the kitchen island, turn right again and go to the back of the island.
Pick up the Martini glass to the left of the head of lettuce.
Turn around and go to the refrigerator all the way to the left corner of the kitchen.
Place the Martini glass in the middle of the top shelf of the refrigerator, wait a moment for the glass to chill, then remove the Martini glass from the refrigerator.  .
Turn to your right and go to the bottom cabinet, to the left of the stove.
Place the glass in the bottom cabinet to the left of the stove.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold Martini glass in the cabinet.
